reviews.text: The food was excellent, so was the service. The ambiance was "interesting" as the restaurant shares a space with an ax throwing business.
The food was food, it's that simple. Their NY style rice over chicken and their butter chicken was exceptional. It's the perfect take away restaurant....
Got takeout. Very good Indian food - the tikka masala was excellent but the naan was a little hard. Overall I would recommend but more of a take out place.
